node.text:
Some of the many background paintings I did for Trese on Netflix! Comes out June 11 📺

Super honored to contribute to this series and to paint the city I was born in! 🇵🇭

I'm excited for the world to experience our deep Filipino mythology, folklore...and horror. 💀

check out the behind the scenes trailer here:

https://youtu.be/BwhCGO6XI9g

Salamat Jojo Aguilar and Jay Hong for bringing me on the project 🙌

#conceptart #trese #illustration #filipino #horror #fantasy  #philippines #netflix #anime #animation #landscape #city #manila #art
